Usage: pdp [OPTIONS] COMMAND [ARGS]...

  This is the official Pureinsights Discovery Platform CLI.

Options:
  --namespace TEXT  Namespace in which the PDP components are running. Default
                    is "pdp".
  --profile TEXT    Configuration profile to load specific configurations from
                    pdp.ini. Default is "DEFAULT"
  --help            Show this message and exit.

Commands:
  config  Contains all the commands to help you manage the entities on PDP.
  health  This command is used to know if PDP-CLI has been installed...
